 the entry with natural light. The flowing floorplan unfolds into an impressive series of living and entertaining zones, each crafted to suit the rhythm of busy family life. An open-plan living, meals and family area sits at the heart of the home, complemented by a dedicated formal dining space and a huge rumpus room-perfect for weekend gatherings, kids' play or versatile everyday living.\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E\u003Cbr\u002F\u003EMovie lovers will adore the purpose-built theatre room positioned at the front of the home, complete with tiered seating and a full projector setup to elevate every movie night into a cinema experience. Centrally located and beautifully appointed, the kitchen offers a superb layout with abundant storage, stainless steel appliances, expansive bench space and both high-bar and breakfast bar seating-all ready to cater for everything from weekday meals to festive celebrations.\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E\u003Cbr\u002F\u003EMultiple sliding doors create seamless indoor-outdoor connection, opening onto an expansive decked alfresco area. With both sun-soaked and covered zones, it's a standout space for entertaining family and friends while enjoying tranquil views across the large, fully fenced backyard. Designed for low-maintenance living and framed by easy-care landscaping, this is a haven for kids, pets and relaxed outdoor enjoyment.\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E\u003Cbr\u002F\u003EPrivately tucked away from the living zones, four well-sized bedrooms ensure restful retreat for each family member. The master suite impresses with a walk-in wardrobe and a stylish ensuite featuring dual vanities and sleek black fittings. Three additional bedrooms are serviced by a modern family bathroom with a separate bath and shower, while a dedicated study\u002Fhome office adds excellent flexibility for work or study from home. Additional features include a separate laundry with storage, reverse-cycle air-conditioning and a double remote garage.\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E\u003Cbr\u002F\u003ESet in a peaceful, family-friendly street, this exceptional home offers unmatched lifestyle convenience. St Teresa's Catholic Primary School, bus stops, playgrounds, bike paths and walking tracks are all within walking distance. Just moments away, you'll also enjoy quick access to childcare facilities, major shopping centres, additional schools and fantastic transport options.\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E\u003Cbr\u002F\u003EOrmeau is a thriving suburb offering a safe, family-friendly environment with a strong sense of community. Streets are quiet, well-maintained, and patrolled, giving residents peace of mind. Convenience is a hallmark, with easy access to local shops, schools, parks, and public transport, while major highways connect you to Brisbane and the Gold Coast in under an hour. The area is experiencing significant growth, with new residential developments, shopping precincts, and infrastructure projects enhancing lifestyle options and property values. Combining safety, accessibility, and ongoing expansion, Ormeau is an ideal location for families, investors, and anyone seeking a balanced, modern lifestyle.\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E\u003Cbr\u002F\u003EMove-in ready and designed for effortless family living, this beautifully appointed home is an opportunity not to be missed in one of Ormeau's most desirable pockets.\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E\u003Cbr\u002F\u003EProperty Features:\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E- 699m² fully fenced block with landscaped surrounds\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E- Contemporary single-level design in a quiet, family-friendly street\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E- Open-plan living, formal dining and meals area\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E- Oversized rumpus room for additional living versatility\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E- Separate theatre room with tiered seating and projector\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E- Large kitchen with fantastic bench space, breakfast bar seating and stainless steel appliances\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E- Expansive decked alfresco entertaining with both covered and open-air options\u003Cbr\u002F