, offering excellent flow, separation, and functionality for modern living.\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E\u003Cbr\u002F\u003EAt the heart of the home is the stunning designer kitchen, where style meets performance. A striking waterfall stone benchtop anchors the space, complemented by well-designed cabinetry and quality finishes. Cooking is effortless with the 900mm gas cooktop and 900mm oven, providing ample space and power for entertaining, family meals, or passionate home cooks. Perfectly positioned, the kitchen forms the hub of the home, with the lounge and dining areas located on either side, enhancing both connection and versatility.\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E\u003Cbr\u002F\u003EThe lounge is cosy yet light-filled, offering a welcoming space to relax while still enjoying an abundance of natural light. The dining area is generous in size and highly adaptable, easily accommodating larger gatherings and flowing directly out to the north-facing entertaining deck, making indoor-outdoor living seamless.\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E\u003Cbr\u002F\u003EThroughout the home, thoughtful inclusions elevate both comfort and style. Floor-to-ceiling sheer curtains, tinted windows, and near-new wool carpet feature across multiple rooms, providing privacy, softness, and excellent light control while enhancing the overall sense of warmth and refinement.\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E\u003Cbr\u002F\u003EOn cooler days, the pellet fire becomes an inviting focal point within the living space, delivering warmth and atmosphere with the ease of a single button. Paired with reverse-cycle air conditioning, the home is well equipped for year-round comfort.\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E\u003Cbr\u002F\u003EAccommodation is exceptionally well-zoned, offering privacy and quiet separation. The master suite is positioned away from the remaining bedrooms, creating a true retreat. It features a custom-built walk-in wardrobe with bespoke joinery and a spacious ensuite designed for comfort and ease. The remaining bedrooms are well-proportioned, each with built-in wardrobes and convenient access to the main bathroom, which is generously sized and beautifully appointed with a frameless glass shower, floating vanity, and a bath thoughtfully positioned within the space.\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E\u003Cbr\u002F\u003EThe newly renovated laundry is both functional and aesthetic, offering excellent storage and thoughtful design that continues the home's cohesive styling.\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E\u003Cbr\u002F\u003EOutdoors, the home continues to impress. The fully fenced, low-maintenance yard provides privacy and ease of upkeep, while the exposed aggregate driveway offers strong street appeal and ample off-street parking. Multiple outdoor spaces allow you to enjoy the home at different times of day, all while taking in the surrounding outlook and mountain views.\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E\u003Cbr\u002F\u003EImmaculately presented from front to back, this is a home where every detail has been considered, and nothing needs to be done - simply move in and enjoy.\u003Cbr\u002F\u003E\u003Cbr\u002F\u003EKingston remains one of Hobart's most desirable lifestyle locations, offering an exceptional balance of convenience and community. With schools, shops, parks, cafes, and essential amenities close by, and Hobart CBD easily accessible, it's easy to see why families, professionals, and downsizers alike are drawn to the area. 18 Tetratheca Drive delivers not just a beautifully finished home, but a lifestyle defined by comfort, ease, and connection to its surroundings.\\\",\\\"media\\\":{\\\"mainImage\\\":{\\\"templatedUrl\\\":\\\"https:\u002F\u002Fi2.au.reastatic.net\u002F{size}\u002F036d51beabd4cd2a45583dcd99607b492fbc2c15ffb13bc09a04f17fefbaee78\u002Fimage.jpg\\\",\\\"__typename\\\":\\\"Image\\\"},\\\"images\\\":[{\\\"__typename\\\":\\\"Image\\\",\\\"templatedUrl\\\":\\\"https:\u002F\u002Fi2.au.reastatic.net\u002F{size}\u002F036d51beabd4cd2a45583dcd99607b492fbc2c15ffb13bc09a04f17fefbaee78\u002Fimage.jpg\\\"},{\\\"__typename\\\":\\\"Image\